data.description: Custom home w/a separate guest house situated on 5 acres overlooking the City of Burnet and views of the hill country. The main house is 5 BR 3 BTH with an office nook, ceramic tile and ceramic tile wood pattern in common areas, one bedroom with wood flooring, kitchen features tile counters, and custom cabinets incl built in china cabinet. Separate guest house features 1/1 home w/granite, all appliances incl W/D and stained concrete floors sharing a wall and covered front porch with a gameroom w/half bath for entertaining. Both homes have sprinkler system in front yard. Main home is all elec except gas FP and guest house is gas & on demand water heater. Truly a fabulous place for entertaining or rent out the guest house...multiple uses.
